methods.getStaticSymbolTable:
Get a static Table view of this SymbolTableSource's symbol table, providing a many:1 or 1:1 mapping of
 unique long identifiers to the symbol values in this source.

:param sourceIndex: (io.deephaven.db.v2.utils.Index) - The Index whose keys must be mappable via the result Table's identifier
                         column
:param useLookupCaching: (boolean) - Whether symbol lookups performed to generate the symbol table should apply caching
:return: (io.deephaven.db.tables.Table) The symbol table
methods.getSymbolTable:
Get a Table view of this SymbolTableSource's symbol table, providing a many:1 or 1:1 mapping of unique
 long identifiers to the symbol values in this source.

 The result will be refreshing if table is a refreshing DynamicTable.

:param sourceTable: (io.deephaven.db.v2.QueryTable) - The QueryTable whose Index keys must be mappable via the result
                         Table's identifier column
:param useLookupCaching: (boolean) - Whether symbol lookups performed to generate the symbol table should apply caching
:return: (io.deephaven.db.tables.Table) The symbol table

text:
Interface for ColumnSources that can provide a Table view of their
 symbol tables, providing a many:1 or 1:1 mapping of unique long identifiers to the symbol values in this
 source.
 Such sources are also expected to be reinterpretable (ColumnSource.allowsReinterpret(Class)) as
 long ColumnSources of the same identifiers.
